race.comment: PARABOLE RICO (2) comes off a (25.69) win last time, scoring by a head in a Grade 4/5 over 460m at Geelong. Has three wins already from this draw. Looks a leading chance on best. AMRON SAMMY (4) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at The Meadows. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. AMRON MICK (6) is worth forgiving for his last effort when sixth (31.43) at The Meadows over 525m. Strike rate this course strong having won four of six tries. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. HOLDEN BALE (1) has strong credentials over this journey.
